title: 3 and Out - Manning Bros MNF Gig, Untradeable Deshaun Watson, Cali CFB Prospect Exodus; Top 3 NFL Moves to Watch
itunes:title: 3 and Out - Manning Bros MNF Gig, Untradeable Deshaun Watson, Cali CFB Prospect Exodus; Top 3 NFL Moves to Watch
description:
In this episode, John reacts to Peyton and Eli Manning taking a gig doing an alternate Monday Night Football broadcast, why Deshaun Watson is untradeable in 2021, why NIL won't solve the exodus of top Cali prospects to out of state schools, and his top 3 offseason moves that John wants to see play out in 2021.
